Other countries with notable overnight changes to keep an eye on:
- Uzbekistan: day 1 of reporting 4 cases, day 2-8 cases;
- Uruguay: in 24 hours almost 5-fold increase from 6 cases to 29 cases;
- Turkey: more than doubled in 24 hours from 12 to 29 cases;
- Honduras: doubled from 3 to 6 cases over 24 hours;
- Mongolia: went from 1 to 4 cases in 24 hours;
- Channel Islands: went from 3 to 6 cases in 24 hours;
- Ukraine: went from 3 to 7 cases in 24 hours;
- Jordan: more than doubled in 24 hours from 12 to 29 cases;
- Andorra: doubled from 4 to 9 cases in 24 hours with more than 2 weeks steady at 1 case;
- Dominican Republic: almost doubled in 24 hours from 11 to 21 cases;
- Armenia: almost doubled in 24 hours from 28 to 52 cases;
- Monaco: 3.5 times increase in 24 hours after 2 weeks of 1 an 2 cases, went from 2 to 9 cases

Included in the list of countries with 30 or more cases but noteworthy for rapid increase in 24 hours
- Chile: more than doubled in 24 hours from 75 to 156 cases
- Pakistan: over 3-fold increase in 24 hours from 53 to 184 cases

Total number of reported deaths: 7171
Deaths outside mainland China: 3945 [including 7 from the Diamond Princess cruise ship]

